children.name: INSERT INTO "offer_range_excluded_products" ("range_id", "product_id") VALUES (511, 905) ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING

SELECT 1 AS "a" FROM "catalogue_product" WHERE (NOT ("catalogue_product"."id" IN (SELECT U0."id" FROM "catalogue_product" U0 INNER JOIN "offer_range_excluded_products" U1 ON (U0."id" = U1."product_id") WHERE U1."range_id" = 511)) AND "catalogue_product"."id" = 905) LIMIT 1

SELECT "catalogue_product"."id", "catalogue_product"."structure", "catalogue_product"."is_public", "catalogue_product"."upc", "catalogue_product"."parent_id", "catalogue_product"."title", "catalogue_product"."slug", "catalogue_product"."description", "catalogue_product"."meta_title", "catalogue_product"."meta_description", "catalogue_product"."product_class_id", "catalogue_product"."rating", "catalogue_product"."date_created", "catalogue_product"."date_updated", "catalogue_product"."is_discountable" FROM "catalogue_product" WHERE NOT ("catalogue_product"."id" IN (SELECT U0."id" FROM "catalogue_product" U0 INNER JOIN "offer_range_excluded_products" U1 ON (U0."id" = U1."product_id") WHERE U1."range_id" = 511)) ORDER BY "catalogue_product"."date_created" DESC
